<h3>Additional Supporting Materials</h3>
<div class='slide_deck_embed'></div>
<div class='other_resources'><p><a href="http://rarar.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://rarar.com</a></p></div>
</div>
<div class='idea-block idea-takeaways'>
<h3>Takeaways</h3>
<ol id='questions_answered'>
<li>What is cognitive user experience?</li>
<li>How can we make user experience cognitive?</li>
<li>What are the implications for design and designers?</li>
</ol>
</div>
